Must be able to stream audio from YouTube (must not output video)
Must be able to play audio in background
Must be lightweight (can be played without YT page open)
Must be able to add songs to playlists using YT URLs with your custom name
Must be able to save playlists (either to an account or to browser custom data)
Must be able to play, pause, change volume, skip track, seek
Must be able to add multiple playlists, as well as rearrange them, and delete them
